data.description: Won't last long!! Cute 4 bedroom, 2 bath. Large family room with fireplace is open to kitchen and dining area. It has an enclosed garage offers many options for additional office, exercise, playroom, or den. It also has a mudroom, walk-in  pantry off of the laundry room. This sits on a level corner lot and is close to all three schools, shopping and local events. This beautiful home has many upgrades. (All new windows, laminate flooring, new paint)  The spacious backyard is fenced and has a storage building with power. This home has an attached metal carport and is a must see.
